sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Platform as Platform Ingress<br/>(kube-rbac-proxy / Gateway API)
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant vLLMEmb as vLLM Embedding Server<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI FMS<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Milvus as Milvus<br/>(inline or remote)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Inference Request (vLLM Backend)
    Client->>Platform: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Platform-managed
    Platform->>LS: HTTP 8321/TCP<br/>plaintext
    LS->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: API Token<br/>Encryption: Configurable TLS
    vLLM-->>LS: Inference Response
    LS->>PG: Log inference<br/>5432/TCP<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>LS: OK
    LS-->>Platform: JSON Response
    Platform-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Safety Evaluation
    Client->>Platform: POST /v1/safety/run-shield<br/>Auth: Platform-managed
    Platform->>LS: HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS->>TrustyAI: Safety evaluation request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Configurable SSL
    TrustyAI-->>LS: Safety evaluation result
    LS-->>Platform: Safety Response
    Platform-->>Client: Safety Response

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 3: RAG with Vector Store
    Client->>Platform: POST /v1/agents/create<br/>Auth: Platform-managed
    Platform->>LS: HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS->>vLLMEmb: Embedding request<br/>Auth: API Token
    vLLMEmb-->>LS: Embedding vectors
    LS->>Milvus: Vector store/search<br/>HTTP/gRPC<br/>Auth: Token
    Milvus-->>LS: Similar documents
    LS->>vLLM: Inference with context<br/>Auth: API Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Generated response
    LS-->>Platform: Agent Response
    Platform-->>Client: Agent Response

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Model Evaluation (LM Eval)
    Client->>Platform: POST /v1/eval/run<br/>Auth: Platform-managed
    Platform->>LS: HTTP 8321/TCP
    LS->>K8sAPI: Create eval Job (USE_K8S=true)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>LS: Job created
    LS->>vLLM: Evaluation inference<br/>Auth: API Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Inference results
    LS-->>Platform: Evaluation Results
    Platform-->>Client: Evaluation Results
